==English==

===Etymology===
<!--Etym. is from Websters 1913; remove this if updated -->
OE. [[fauconer]], OF. [[falconier]], [[fauconier]], F. [[fauconnier]]. See [[falcon|Falcon]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
<!--Def is from Websters 1913; remove this if updated -->
#  A person who breeds or trains [[hawk]]s for taking birds or game.
<!--Def is from Websters 1913; remove this if updated -->
#  One who [[follow]]s the sport of [[fowling]] with hawks. 

